race.comment: They'll go like the clappers in this. BOSSED UP (19) has been right there at the past few outings and is drawn to get a soft run in transit from gate two. Capable of playing a big role. CASPERNOVA (2) is yet to miss a quinella spot in six spins around this circuit and looms as a major threat with the added aid of the claim. MISTER BIANCO (8) will be better over further but has a touch of class on his side and has drawn to get a lovely soft run. JOHN RAMBO (9) is a noted performer fresh and two trials should have him ready to fire.
